<p>
The word chambray is used 39 times in 26 Stephen King novels, novellas and short-stories.<br>
Given there are 194 novels, novellas and short-stories, that means 168 do NOT contain the word chambray.<br>
22 of his 62 novels have the word chambray. That's 35%.<br>
Anything published after Later in 2021 is not included.<br>
